data.text:
Awards & Honors

Big 12 Commissioner's Honor Roll (S22, F22)

Academic All-Big 12 Rookie Team (2023)

2023

Saw action in five games before electing to transfer ... saw most of his action on special teams ... had two receptions for 12 yards against Oklahoma ... finished Cyclone career playing in nine games with three receptions for 14 yards.

2022

Played in four games and redshirted ... saw action at receiver and on special teams ... made first career catch against Ohio.

High School

Chose Iowa State over Indiana, Kansas State and Maryland … a four-star recruit by 247Sports and Rivals … three-star recruit by On3 … listed as the 42nd-best wide receiver and the No. 316 player in the nation by 247Sports … listed as the 37th-best wide receiver and the No. 231 player nationally by Rivals … second-team all-state selection in 2020 and a two-time all-conference pick… recorded 63 receptions for 830 yards and 10 touchdowns as a senior while helping his team to a 14-1 record and its first state championship appearance in school history … had 43 catches for 804 yards and 13 touchdowns as a junior … caught 39 passes for 664 yards and nine touchdowns as a sophomore … also returned kicks and punts … tallied 145 receptions for 2,298 yards and 32 touchdowns during his high school career … coached by Jayson Roberts.
